        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aron Schuhmann",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aronschuhmann@gmail.com"
            },
            "text": "And so that, uh, yeah, so that's, uh, so this is, I'm realizing is kind of taking a step back and being like, this is sort of where I've developed some expertise and realizing there are some specific needs of companies at this stage and trying to find like where I can have, you know, an impact with what I've learned.",
