        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aron Schuhmann",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aronschuhmann@gmail.com"
            },
            "text": "And I think there's an, it's an interesting time for early startups that I think they can just in general, take functions aside, they can grow revenue really lean.",
