        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aron Schuhmann",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aronschuhmann@gmail.com"
            },
            "text": "So I think there's a new way that you can fund and then monetize a startup in a really efficient way.",
