        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aron Schuhmann",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aronschuhmann@gmail.com"
            },
            "text": "Um, whether that's a demand of capital, who's really pushing that or just because it's possible, you know, but I think it is possible.",
