        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aron Schuhmann",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aronschuhmann@gmail.com"
            },
            "text": "Some companies are showing it and I think it has an interesting knock on effect for go to market could be, one, I think it could be lean into, I think it could also be not all in-house.",
