        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aron Schuhmann",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aronschuhmann@gmail.com"
            },
            "text": "You may be able to push a company and just really focus your in-house resources on product, engineering, and adjacent marketing functions that are hard to have outside.",
