        },
        {
            "speaker": {
                "display_name": "Aron Schuhmann",
                "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "aronschuhmann@gmail.com"
            },
            "text": "And I think that for the businesses providing those services, it's also a good time to deliver those services with a high margin, given sort of like the tools that are available.",
